Susan Strasberg https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Susan_Strasberg 0 Susan Elizabeth Strasberg (May 22, 1938 – January 21, 1999) was an American stage, film, and television actress, the daughter of the drama coach Lee Strasberg. She was nominated for a Tony Award when she was 18 years old.
